# Config credentials (never commit API keys). The `src/config/defaults/
# credentials/` exception holds embedded templates with placeholder
# values like `REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_KEY` — those *are* tracked, since
# they're shipped boilerplate, not real secrets.
credentials/
!src/config/defaults/credentials/

